#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.48:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Gahapativagga"
msgstr "5. Householders"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Lokāyatikasutta"
msgstr "48. A Cosmologist"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.48:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "Then a brahmin cosmologist went up to the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn12.48:1.3"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinno kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side he said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamatthī”ti?"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, does all exist?”"

msgctxt "sn12.48:2.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbamatthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, jeṭṭhametaṃ lokāyataṃ”."
msgstr "“‘All exists’: this is the oldest cosmology, brahmin.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:3.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṃ natthī”ti?"
msgstr "“Then does all not exist?”"

msgctxt "sn12.48:3.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbaṃ natthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, dutiyametaṃ lokāyataṃ”."
msgstr "“‘All doesn’t exist’: this is the second cosmology."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:4.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamekattan”ti?"
msgstr "“Well, is all a unity?”"

msgctxt "sn12.48:4.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbamekattan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, tatiyametaṃ lokāyataṃ”."
msgstr "“‘All is a unity’: this is the third cosmology."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:5.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṃ puthuttan”ti?"
msgstr "“Then is all a plurality?”"

msgctxt "sn12.48:5.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbaṃ puthuttan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, catutthametaṃ lokāyataṃ."
msgstr "“‘All is a plurality’: this is the fourth cosmology."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:6.1"
msgid ""
"Ete te, brāhmaṇa, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathāgato dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr ""
"Avoiding these two extremes, the Realized One teaches by the middle way:"

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.2"
msgid "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "‘Ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.3"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.4"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.5"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.6"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.48:6.7"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.48:7.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin cosmologist said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn12.48:7.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn12.48:7.3"
msgid "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.48:7.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
